creator: Reflecting Him Ministries
descriptionHtml:
Reflecting Him Ministries is a safe community where you can come just as you are, right where you are with the Lord, and connect heart to heart with both God and other believers.

Give God 15 minutes! Join us for communion and experience first-hand the Blessing of God’s Presence, the transforming power of His Word, and the limitless healing power of the Holy Spirit. God knows exactly what you need and is faithful so that when you come to Him, you will come away with answers to your prayers, words of wisdom or guidance, solutions and strategies for your life and relationships, and the healing you have been longing for. He wants you to know Him and the power of His Resurrection. So enter into Communion with Him and receive:

Healing for your anxious mind, your wounded heart, your hurting body, and your crushed spirit

Encouragement to hold you up when you can't stand, to walk with you when the road is hard, and to cheer you on to the good future that God has for you

Empowerment to conquer whatever mountain you may face, to shatter strongholds, and to change destructive habits and mindsets

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- New Media Search Experience with support for Speakers, Topics, and Scripture tags
- New Related media section on Media Items shows other media tagged with the same Topics
- Enhanced user profile with additional field and a direct integration to our CMS for Messaging Customers
- Misc. bug fixes and improvements.
